Xinjiang Agricultural Machinery Trade Fair 2015 - People's Daily Online

Xinjiang Agricultural Machinery Trade Fair 2015 attracts attention. (Photo by Qi Yaping / Chinanews)

 Xinjiang Agricultural Machinery Trade Fair is a 3-day event being held from August 13 to 15 in Changji, Xinjiang .

 This fair attracts 200 domestic enterprises and international enterprises from France, Germany and other countries. It is a platform for exhibition and communication between domestic and international agricultural machinery, enterprises, scientific research institutes and users.Â 